OL,3,CFormer Post Office top lawyer says he
OL,4,Cis 'deeply sorry' at inquiry
OL,6,FSpeaking at the inquiry on Wednesday,
OL,7,FMr Aujard said he was responsible for
OL,8,Fmanaging a department of lawyers at
OL,9,Fthe Post Office, but highlighted that
OL,10,Fthe investigation into the Post
OL,11,FOffice's review into theft and fraud
OL,12,Fwas already underway before he took on
OL,13,Fthe role.
OL,15,FWhen asked if anybody in the legal
OL,16,Fteam had told him about bugs, errors
OL,17,For defects in the Horizon IT software,
OL,18,FMr Aujard replied with "no, the
OL,19,Fopposite".
