OL,6,F"I was told there were no defects
OL,7,Fapart from the ones mentioned in the
OL,8,Freport," he said.
OL,10,FWhen asked by the judge if he would
OL,11,Fhave needed to know about any issues
OL,12,Fwith the Horizon system, Mr Aujard
OL,13,Fsaid "yes, in circumstances that had a
OL,14,Flegal connection", but that he would
OL,15,Fhave needed to turn to the IT and
OL,16,Ffinance team.
OL,18,F"Are you saying you relied on external
OL,19,Fsources of legal advice?" the judge
OL,20,Fasked.
