OL,4,Cis 'deeply sorry' at inquiry
OL,6,FOver the last few weeks ITV News has
OL,7,Fbroadcast secret recordings which show
OL,8,Fjust how much people at the top of the
OL,9,FPost Office knew about faults with its
OL,10,FHorizon IT system - and how long ago.
OL,11,FIn one of them, its most senior former
OL,12,Flawyer is told by independent
OL,13,Finvestigators that the Post Office had
OL,14,Fpressured sub-postmasters into
OL,15,Fpleading guilty to crimes they didn't
OL,16,Fcommit. He's also told that the Post
OL,17,FOffice has potentially misled the
OL,18,Fcourts. Hundreds of innocent people
OL,19,Fwere convicted.
